name: Lunar Wraith Morgana
description: Morgana is a dark spirit who appears during Lunar Revel—a famed seducer of mortals, monsters, and gods alike. Legend says she ensnares the hearts and minds of her victims before dragging their souls away to an unspeakable purgatory, never to be heard from again.
